 * more flexible compilation configuration
 * add support for CCS, JALV2, BoostC, BoostC++, and BoostBasic compilers
 * support for GPSim 0.22
 * less CPU usage and errors when verifying with serial ICD2 [fix from Steve Moskovchenko]
